at 92nd and Broadway.

24:15.872 --> 24:17.908
-I need a warrant.
-You won't need a warrant.

24:18.124 --> 24:20.365
-I won't need a warrant.
-This is the number.

24:20.585 --> 24:23.873
The call was placed
at exactly 2 pm. yesterday.

24:25.006 --> 24:26.212
-Aram?
-Yes.

24:26.424 --> 24:29.507
I can't stress enough
the urgency of this matter.

24:42.273 --> 24:45.185
Thank you for coming. I--

24:45.401 --> 24:47.016
Tracy, hello.

24:47.236 --> 24:48.567
