I was in a desperate situation.

25:22.271 --> 25:24.432
You saw the marks.
He threatened to kill me.

25:24.649 --> 25:28.938
I tried the police, all the right channels,
and no one lifted a finger.

25:32.532 --> 25:34.272
I'm grateful to you.

25:34.659 --> 25:36.149
I would never betray you.

25:40.915 --> 25:42.075
You--

25:46.212 --> 25:48.168
Hello, Miss Henning?

25:51.217 --> 25:52.957
Miss Henning?

25:55.722 --> 25:57.633
