were murdered by the copycat...

28:29.250 --> 28:30.911
...after they sought help,

28:31.127 --> 28:34.290
Except her. Tracy Solobotkin.

28:34.505 --> 28:36.791
Her husband was the first victim
of our copycat...

28:37.008 --> 28:39.624
