31:44.153 --> 31:46.769
You know, with the cutting, the mess,
I hated it.

31:46.989 --> 31:49.196
But I didn't have a choice.

31:50.367 --> 31:52.153
I'm sick.

31:52.620 --> 31:54.201
I know.

31:54.622 --> 31:58.456
Disgusting.
But that's the way Ron did it.

31:59.210 --> 32:01.667
So I have no choice.

32:02.254 --> 32:04.165
Even from beyond the grave...

32:04.381 --> 32:06.508
...he still pulls the strings.

32:07.176 --> 32:08.837
Okay.

32:10.346 --> 32:12.007
You gotta do what you gotta do.

32:13.182 --> 32:16.800
But can you please,
please just do me one favor?

32:17.645 --> 32:21.263
-Yes?
-Shut the hell up and get it over with.

32:22.024 --> 32:24.686
What? You think I don't know
why you're really doing this?

32:24.902 --> 32:27.018
You think I'm buying
this whole "justice for victims" crap?

32:27.530 --> 32:28.940
Well, it's true.

32:29.573 --> 32:32.406
-You're just like your husband.
-I'm nothing like my husband.

32:32.618 --> 32:36.406
