what you had to do to survive.

34:04.668 --> 34:07.284
-Same as on the boat.
-That was different. That was Tom.

34:07.504 --> 34:09.460
-You tried to stop him.
-But I didn't.

34:10.591 --> 34:12.252
I hesitated.

34:12.468 --> 34:15.801
