38:49.536 --> 38:52.619
Yes, I'm scolding you.
That was foolish. You could've been--

38:52.831 --> 38:55.789
-Ki||ed.
-Exactly that. Killed.

38:56.001 --> 38:59.585
What are you gonna do? Ground me?
Take away my phone privileges?

39:07.679 --> 39:09.385
You were right about the Deer Hunter.

39:09.598 --> 39:11.179
-He was a man.
-And a woman.

39:11.517 --> 39:13.508
We were both half right.

39:14.686 --> 39:16.551
Together, we were right.

39:24.112 --> 39:26.364
I have the Fulcrum.

39:30.994 --> 39:33.610
Tell me what it is,
and I'll tell you where to find it.

39:34.706 --> 39:37.118
I've already told you what I can.

39:37.751 --> 39:39.787
To elaborate would place you
in grave danger.

39:40.003 --> 39:42.210
-I don't need your protection.
-I think you do.

39:42.422 --> 39:45.084
If it weren't for me,
you would have been indicted today.

39:45.300 --> 39:48.007
As it is, you needn't worry
about the harbormaster anymore.

39:48.220 --> 39:49.335
What did you do?

39:49.555 --> 39:52.046
Nobody was hurt,
if that's what you're concerned about.

39:52.516 --> 39:54.552
In fact,
a young man's life was saved.

39:54.768 --> 39:56.759
I don't wanna hear any more.
I'm leaving.

39:56.979 --> 40:00.813
I believe I know the real reason
you don't want me to have the Fulcrum.

40:01.316 --> 40:03.022
That is?

40:03.569 --> 40:05.810
Because you're afraid...

40:06.697 --> 40:10.815
...that once you give it to me,
you'll be of no further use to me...

40:11.159 --> 40:13.445
...and you'll never see me again.
